{"tid":1002141,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【拍拖一年】愛瑪史東孖導演男友蒲頭 正式公開戀情","createTime":"2019-01-30T17:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T17:26:04.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ecdfa5ee5d1b11541d2511de3a686a67d6519730","tid":1002141,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190129/large/1548756289_93e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190129%2Flarge%2F1548756289_93e7.jpg&h=17dee9ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愛瑪史東前年10月爆出有新對象<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190129/large/1548756343_398a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190129%2Flarge%2F1548756343_398a.jpg&h=5b565165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190129/large/1548756343_4dba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190129%2Flarge%2F1548756343_4dba.jpg&h=d9fb82f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愛瑪史東與Dave McCary近日開始高調約會<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190129/large/1548756229_8e4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190129%2Flarge%2F1548756229_8e4d.jpg&h=0eedbbef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩人與畢列谷巴合照<br />\n奧斯卡影后愛瑪史東（Emma Stone）與安德魯加菲（Andrew Garfield）分手後，前年10月爆出有新對象，其男友是《Saturday Night Live》（SNL）編劇兼導演Dave McCary，豈料兩人之後幾乎沒有被拍到拍拖證據，以為這段關係沒有下文，近日兩人開始高調約會，似乎感情已經穩定。<br />\n愛瑪上周曾與Dave McCary結伴睇球賽，昨日的美國演員工會大獎，更孖住男友出席，兩人一同與現場人士合照，正式公開這段戀情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190129/59199859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59199859&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6nqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=15a2d8be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59199859&h=776ff199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190129/59199859</a>"},{"pid":"9c4b6f7939db8f1e9545564b4f63c076ca63d9e6","tid":1002141,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS13awLx8MYQ8v2Gw7N8QcbU3e78JaOgd4qJ-jdAqUuy49CO2cE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcS13awLx8MYQ8v2Gw7N8QcbU3e78JaOgd4qJ-jdAqUuy49CO2cE&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6nqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=3f1fc91d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS13awLx8MYQ8v2Gw7N8QcbU3e78JaOgd4qJ-jdAqUuy49CO2cE</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931d94187ee4f6b4fa53069e1bfa1e2e3a97e869","tid":1002141,"uid":83531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:11:57.000Z","msg":"各自有新戀情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dc94c0ee821c8cd6f053c189aa66b462152190","tid":1002141,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:13:12.000Z","msg":"畢列谷巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b7296017579cb2643df5cfddefc441a65e8031","tid":1002141,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T17:17:27.000Z","msg":"其實荷里活都幾淫亂下<br />\n話就話現代社會愛情觀開放<br />\n之前有單分手半年就同第個結婚 又有散完轉頭又食番圈內 之後又離婚又盛"},{"pid":"086d0f4deb2dcc45c6f663fb61e6f450810860ae","tid":1002141,"uid":115250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40b7296017579cb2643df5cfddefc441a65e8031","tid":1002141,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-